Jeremy,

Yeah, my dad&#39;s bringing over a morse code converter from audio to 
text for the computer.  So, after i get done cutting my grass i will 
try it out and see if i get anything.  If i do that&#39;s great, but if 
not i can still say i tried something different.  I don&#39;t believe 
these ideas are made up by me, so this may work since they put the 
idea in my head.  At least that&#39;s how i feel about it anyway.

-Steve H.



--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com, Early Cuyler &lt;ecuyler@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt; Steve, I&#39;d like to think that if our spirit friends wish to 
communicate with us, they will use whatever resources available to 
get through. So it&#39;s certainly feasible to think they can use morse 
code.
&gt; 
&gt; Jeremy
