files 
&gt; and played them in a sequence and recorded it, it consists of tone 
&gt; frequencies ranging from 100hz, 250hz, 440hz, 1khz and 10khz.  They 
&gt; were 5 second clips of each and than i ran it through EvpMaker and 
it 
&gt; sounds like morse code, but i have to brush up on it to see if it 
makes 
&gt; any sense.  Is it possible for them to communicate through morse 
code?  
&gt; I&#39;ve attached a 30 second clip of the example running it through 
&gt; EvpMaker.  I&#39;ll also attach my original tone file i created.
